293
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:19,800
Let's go.

294
00:12:19,920 --> 00:12:20,360
I...

295
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:21,560
-Great Madam!
-Mother.

296
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:24,120
What if we bring her

297
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,600
to our house outside the city?

298
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,520
That will serve as a punishment for her,

299
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,200
and the Xu family won't appear heartless

300
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:30,200
towards servants.

301
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,160
Thank you, Great Madam.

302
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,320
Thank you, Second Madam.

303
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,160
Stand up.

304
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:41,880
Let's go.

305
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,640
Shiyi.

306
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,520
You just married into the family,

307
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:51,600
there are many things
you still don't know.

308
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:52,920
So

309
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:56,600
Lianfang will manage the household affairs for now.

310
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:59,200
After you slowly become familiar
with the house rules,

311
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,400
