315
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,960
I know that it's difficult for you.

316
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:11,280
Just do it for the Xu family

317
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,680
and for Lingyi.

318
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:15,720
Stop declining.

319
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,680
Yes, Great Madam.

320
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:25,640
I'm sorry about this, Your Ladyship.

321
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:36,680
Great Madam.

322
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,680
We got the Sichuan brocade
from His Majesty back.

323
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:41,160
That's great.

324
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:43,360
This Sichuan brocade is so intricate.

325
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:45,560
Give me a few to make my clothes.

326
00:13:45,640 --> 00:13:48,240
Of course we can't neglect you.

327
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:50,360
Ask the servants

328
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,200
