the bird's nest porridge.

366
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:17,560
I've already eaten outside.

367
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:21,480
Zhun.

368
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:24,240
Zhun, slow down.

369
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,320
Zhun.

370
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:29,040
Are you done with your homework?

371
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:30,600
Zhun.

372
00:15:34,920 --> 00:15:37,160
You should be in your morning class.
