378
00:15:46,760 --> 00:15:47,840
so he especially came to see you.

379
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:48,600
Shut up.

380
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:52,880
Come with me.

381
00:15:56,040 --> 00:15:56,720
Stand here.

382
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:00,480
Do the horse stance.

383
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:08,200
Lower.

384
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,120
You're a man.

385
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:17,920
Why are you crying?

386
00:16:20,800 --> 00:16:21,760
It's just been a short while,

387
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:22,800
and you can't endure it anymore.

388
00:16:23,520 --> 00:16:24,840
Since ancient times, those who want
to accomplish great things

389
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:26,240
must experience frustrations

390
00:16:26,400 --> 00:16:27,240
and physical exhaustion first.

391
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:29,160
You can't even do the horse stance well.

392
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:30,480
How can you accomplish great things?

393
00:16:35,400 --> 00:16:36,240
-Hey.
-Zhun.

394
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:38,400
Why are you so strict

395
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:39,520
towards such a small child?

396
00:16:40,440 --> 00:16:41,240
He's just a child.

397
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:42,960
He's not your soldier.

398
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:44,720
I... when I was

399
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:45,560
at his age,

400
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:46,920
I wasn't as squeamish as him.

401
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:48,200
That's nonsense.

402
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:50,640
When you were his age,

