405
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,760
I was so scared that I asked
the imperial physician to check on you.

406
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:58,040
I thought you got some sort of illness.

407
00:17:01,280 --> 00:17:01,840
Mother.

408
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:03,200
You're mistaken.

409
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:04,200
That was Lingkuan.

410
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:09,640
Mother, it wasn't me.

411
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:10,480
Lingkuan.

412
00:17:11,080 --> 00:17:12,680
Think about it carefully first.

413
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:19,920
Mother, I was mistaken.

414
00:17:20,080 --> 00:17:20,960
That was me.

415
00:17:21,080 --> 00:17:22,160
When it was snowing
and Lingyi had a fever,

416
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:23,400
