417
00:17:34,600 --> 00:17:35,840
Zhun.

418
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:36,800
Come.

419
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:38,640
Come to grandmother.

420
00:17:38,840 --> 00:17:42,440
Let's go back to the room
and have some cake.

421
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:43,520
Let's have cake.

422
00:17:43,600 --> 00:17:44,840
Your Ladyship, I didn't expect

423
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:46,480
that His Lordship would be so naughty
when he was little.

424
00:17:55,560 --> 00:17:57,440
His Lordship is too strict.

425
00:17:57,560 --> 00:17:58,240
Zhun

426
00:17:58,400 --> 00:17:59,840
is his legitimate son after all.

427
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,520
