430
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,440
Originally, I wanted to bring him back

431
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:08,120
to the Western Lateral Court
to take good care of him.

432
00:18:08,360 --> 00:18:09,880
But mother wants

433
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:11,680
to continue raising him by her side.

434
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:14,040
I think she can't bear to part with him.

435
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:18,080
Your Ladyship, that's Concubine Qiao.

436
00:18:24,800 --> 00:18:25,480
What's the matter?

437
00:18:25,520 --> 00:18:26,240
You want to go over there

438
00:18:26,360 --> 00:18:27,120
and argue with her?

439
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:27,840
Then...

440
00:18:28,360 --> 00:18:29,920
She's managing the household affairs now.

441
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:30,680
If she charges you

442
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:31,960
for insubordination,

443
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:33,120
I can't help you.

444
00:18:47,999 --> 00:18:48,640
Your Ladyship.

445
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:49,880
You worked so hard

446
00:18:49,999 --> 00:18:51,080
to give this to Zhun.

447
00:18:51,199 --> 00:18:52,719
Concubine Qiao does't respect you

448
00:18:52,719 --> 00:18:53,479
at all.

449
00:18:53,719 --> 00:18:55,440
She and His Lordship
are fond of each other.

450
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,800
Originally, she could have been
the legal wife of the Xu family.

451
00:18:57,920 --> 00:18:59,120
Yet because of Yuanniang,

452
00:18:59,239 --> 00:19:00,760
she's a concubine now.

453
00:19:00,999 --> 00:19:03,080
It's understandable for her to hate me.

454
00:19:03,199 --> 00:19:04,199
So we'll just let her

455
00:19:04,320 --> 00:19:05,880
