any trouble myself,

457
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,520
I won't let others bully me either.

458
00:19:12,480 --> 00:19:14,960
This isn't a peaceful and quiet place.

459
00:19:15,080 --> 00:19:15,720
From now on, you and I

460
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:17,200
must be extra careful.

461
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,320
How troublesome.

462
00:19:19,440 --> 00:19:21,360
You just married into this family.

463
00:19:22,280 --> 00:19:23,480
Silly girl.

464
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:24,720
Don't worry.

465
00:19:24,800 --> 00:19:25,840
You have me.

466
00:19:26,240 --> 00:19:26,680
Go.

467
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:28,520
Bring this perfume satchel to Nanny Tao.

468
00:19:38,320 --> 00:19:39,520
Have you heard?

469
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:42,240
Last night, His Lordship slept
at the Western Lateral Court

470
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:43,320
the whole night.

471
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:49,480
A man discards the old

472
00:19:49,680 --> 00:19:51,880
