Greetings.

496
00:20:43,440 --> 00:20:44,840
You're here.

497
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:47,240
I'll sit down first.

498
00:20:47,840 --> 00:20:48,960
Have a seat.

499
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,160
Jade.

500
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:54,080
Today is the first day

501
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:56,240
