518
00:21:30,080 --> 00:21:32,480
You're the descendant
of a prominent family indeed.

519
00:21:32,760 --> 00:21:33,680
You're different.

520
00:21:33,840 --> 00:21:35,200
You've seen a lot and have
a broad range of knowledge.

521
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:37,680
