00:23:15,080 --> 00:23:16,240
manage the household affairs.

565
00:23:16,440 --> 00:23:17,480
Isn't Great Madam

566
00:23:17,520 --> 00:23:18,800
playing favorites?

567
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:20,680
I didn't marry into the Xu family

568
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:21,760
for that purpose.

569
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:22,880
It's fine.

570
00:23:25,520 --> 00:23:26,920
Your Ladyship, I've already found out

571
00:23:27,080 --> 00:23:28,240
what you wanted me to check.

572
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:29,360
Tell me.

573
00:23:29,800 --> 00:23:30,560
Great Madam

574
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:32,520
wakes up at 5 a.m.

575
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:35,000
So everyone will greet her from 7 a.m.

576
00:23:35,120 --> 00:23:37,200
to a little past 9 a.m.

577
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:39,280
Then she'll go to the abbey
to light incense.

578
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,600
She'll eat at lunchtime,

579
00:23:41,680 --> 00:23:42,720
then in the afternoon,

580
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:44,840
Great Madam will
play with Zhun for a while

581
00:23:44,960 --> 00:23:46,040
or find Concubine Qiao

582
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:47,640
and Fifth Madam to play cards.

583
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:49,320
She'll eat dinner
between 5 p.m. to 7 p.m.

584
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:51,320
After dinner, she'll take a walk
in the yard.

585
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,720
