586
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:54,880
Thank you, Amber.

587
00:23:55,840 --> 00:23:57,040
You're welcome, Your Ladyship.

588
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:58,640
It's part of my job.

589
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:01,160
As for the other concubines,

590
00:24:01,360 --> 00:24:02,360
I heard

591
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:03,960
that His Lordship is always
on the battlefield,

592
00:24:04,080 --> 00:24:05,280
and he neglects his wives.

593
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:07,760
So none of the three concubines are favored.

594
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:09,600
None of them are favored?

595
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:11,480
Concubines Wen and Qin

596
00:24:11,600 --> 00:24:13,160
have been with His Lordship
for many years,

597
00:24:13,280 --> 00:24:14,280
but their situations

598
00:24:14,400 --> 00:24:15,600
are different.

599
00:24:15,960 --> 00:24:17,440
I heard that when His Lordship

600
00:24:17,560 --> 00:24:19,280
was battling at the border,

601
00:24:19,480 --> 00:24:22,080
the battle was very difficult
because the logistics were bad.

602
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:23,320
The Wen family donated

603
00:24:23,440 --> 00:24:24,520
a lot of money and provisions

604
00:24:24,640 --> 00:24:26,440
to help His Lordship pull through.

605
00:24:26,560 --> 00:24:27,480
Since then,

606
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:28,640
His Lordship made Concubine Wen

607
00:24:28,720 --> 00:24:30,080
his concubine.

608
00:24:30,840 --> 00:24:32,840
It seems like the Wen family
grabbed the opportunity

609
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:34,160
to get connected to the Xu family
in marriage.

610
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:36,560
Concubine Qin

611
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:37,640
was originally the maid

612
00:24:37,760 --> 00:24:39,000
of Great Madam.

613
00:24:39,080 --> 00:24:41,120
Great Madam likes her for being
docile and thoughtful,

614
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:43,440
so she sent him to serve His Lordship.

615
00:24:43,600 --> 00:24:45,880
One time, His Lordship was wounded
and went into a coma.

616
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:47,920
Concubine Qin was the one who stayed
with His Lordship

617
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:49,760
and took care of him
for a period of time.

618
00:24:49,880 --> 00:24:51,560
After His Lordship woke up,

619
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:52,880
Great Madam decided

620
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:54,600
to let him take her as his concubine.

621
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:56,280
But regardless if it's Concubine Wen

622
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:57,680
or Concubine Qin,

623
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:58,400
it seems like

624
00:24:58,560 --> 00:25:00,360
they're not favored by His Lordship.

625
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:03,280
That's strange.

626
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:04,520
Forget about Concubine Wen

627
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:05,600
and Concubine Qin,

628
00:25:05,800 --> 00:25:07,880
why is Concubine Qiao
in the same situation?

629
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:09,560
Great Madam and Madam Qiao

630
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:11,080
are cousins.

631
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:12,440
The Xu and Qiao families

632
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:13,760
are also close to each other.

633
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:14,720
Yes.

634
00:25:15,120 --> 00:25:16,320
But...

635
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:18,200
I'm not sure either.

636
00:25:25,800 --> 00:25:27,480
His Lordship doesn't seem like

637
00:25:27,640 --> 00:25:28,680
a man

638
00:25:28,680 --> 00:25:29,960
with no desires.

639
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:32,840
Is there a special reason?

640
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:37,560
His Lordship is always
on the battlefield.

641
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:38,720
Could it be

642
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:40,960
that he has a hidden illness?

643
00:25:41,800 --> 00:25:42,800
Don't speak nonsense.

644
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:46,440
Your Ladyship.

645
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:48,360
Your Ladyship.

646
00:25:49,320 --> 00:25:50,640
Your Ladyship.

647
00:25:50,760 --> 00:25:51,680
Why haven't you

648
00:25:51,840 --> 00:25:53,040
changed your clothes yet?

649
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:53,800
Hurry.

650
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:54,680
Dongqing, Amber.

651
00:25:54,800 --> 00:25:56,000
Help get Her Ladyship prepared.

652
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:57,440
Get Her Ladyship her clothes.

653
00:25:58,880 --> 00:25:59,680
Your Ladyship.

654
00:25:59,840 --> 00:26:00,640
The concubines

655
00:26:00,800 --> 00:26:03,240
are still waiting to bow to you
and serve you tea.

656
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:04,480
By the way, Your Ladyship,

657
00:26:04,600 --> 00:26:06,160
you must wear some accessories.

658
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:08,080
Oh, right, Your Ladyship.

659
00:26:08,560 --> 00:26:09,560
Your Ladyship.

660
00:26:13,360 --> 00:26:15,160
It's so rare to find southern pearls

661
00:26:15,320 --> 00:26:16,640
of the same size like lotus seeds

662
00:26:16,760 --> 00:26:18,120
and make them into a pair of earrings.

663
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:20,040
Your Ladyship.

664
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:21,400
Concubine Wen

665
00:26:21,520 --> 00:26:23,040
is from a family of merchants.

666
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:24,440
She has sharp eyes.

667
00:26:24,560 --> 00:26:26,560
We can't let her look down on us.

668
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:28,200
Come, Dongqing.

669
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:29,680
Put these on Her Ladyship.

670
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:38,560
Right.

671
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:40,240
This red one.

672
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:43,560
Now, in the entire household affairs,

673
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:44,760
only you

674
00:26:44,880 --> 00:26:46,720
look good in bright red.

675
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:48,760
Dongqing.

676
00:26:48,800 --> 00:26:49,600
Bring the sandalwood boxes

677
00:26:49,720 --> 00:26:50,720
we prepared later.

678
00:26:50,840 --> 00:26:51,720
Those are gifts

679
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:52,840
for the concubines.

680
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:53,480
All right.

681
00:26:53,840 --> 00:26:54,760
Your Ladyship.

682
00:26:54,880 --> 00:26:56,200
You don't need to mind them.

683
00:26:56,320 --> 00:26:58,200
They're just concubines.

684
00:26:58,360 --> 00:27:00,040
If you're pleased,

685
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:01,520
be nice to them.

686
00:27:01,640 --> 00:27:02,640
If not,

687
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:04,200
kick them out.

688
00:27:24,720 --> 00:27:25,800
Madams.

689
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:26,960
Please come in.

690
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:37,120
Greetings, Your Ladyship.

691
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,600
We haven't seen each other for a year.

692
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:44,000
You're still in such high spirits.

693
00:27:44,760 --> 00:27:46,240
Don't tease me, Wen.

694
00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:49,760
Concubines, please offer the tea.

695
00:27:58,560 --> 00:28:00,000
Your Ladyship, please have some tea.

696
00:28:17,040 --> 00:28:18,600
