698
00:28:43,720 --> 00:28:45,080
Be careful.

699
00:28:47,040 --> 00:28:49,920
The one who wants to wear a crown
must bear its weight.

700
00:28:50,080 --> 00:28:51,880
Lianfang, don't worry.

701
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:15,240
Thank you for your gift.

702
00:29:42,040 --> 00:29:43,320
Thank you, Your Ladyship.

703
00:29:48,520 --> 00:29:49,760
In the future,

704
00:29:49,840 --> 00:29:51,600
I hope that we can all get along

705
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:53,480
and share His Lordship's burdens.

706
00:29:53,800 --> 00:29:55,200
All right.

707
00:29:55,320 --> 00:29:56,440
It's getting late.

708
00:29:56,560 --> 00:29:59,040
Go and rest, Concubines.

709
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:07,000
Is there anything else?

710
00:30:08,040 --> 00:30:09,280
We've heard that you want

711
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:11,400
to design some embroideries for fans,

712
00:30:11,520 --> 00:30:13,240
so we've decided

713
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:14,600
to show you

714
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:16,360
our best embroidery items.

715
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:18,160
We hope that they will be able
to help you.

716
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:35,520
This peacock among the flowers design

717
00:30:35,600 --> 00:30:36,840
is exquisite indeed.

718
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:38,640
You have good taste indeed.

719
00:30:38,760 --> 00:30:40,280
I spent 1,000 pounds of gold

720
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:42,280
to buy it
from Color Embroidery Workshop.

721
00:30:42,360 --> 00:30:43,600
I'm afraid

722
00:30:43,720 --> 00:30:45,000
that since you've stayed in Yuhang
for so long,

723
00:30:45,080 --> 00:30:47,080
you're not aware of the preferences
in the capital.

724
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:50,000
That's why we especially brought these
for your reference.

725
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:51,960
It's a rare and precious item.

726
00:30:59,800 --> 00:31:02,320
The stitches are very intricate.

727
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:03,640
It thoroughly expresses

728
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:04,520
the mother's love for her child

729
00:31:04,600 --> 00:31:05,920
between the cow and her calf.

730
00:31:06,040 --> 00:31:07,400
It's amazing.

731
00:31:08,040 --> 00:31:08,960
The relationship between a mother
and a child

732
00:31:09,080 --> 00:31:10,760
is the most selfless one.

733
00:31:10,800 --> 00:31:13,160
That's why it moved you.

734
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:15,840
Shiliu is right.

735
00:31:21,800 --> 00:31:22,560
Your Ladyship.

736
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:24,400
Aside from these, there are more.

737
00:31:24,480 --> 00:31:26,160
Please look at them one by one.

738
00:31:26,320 --> 00:31:27,120
You all

739
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:28,800
are such a great help.

740
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:31,240
Dongqing.

741
00:31:31,760 --> 00:31:33,760
Keep these embroidery items well.

742
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:34,880
After this matter is done,

743
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:36,720
we'll return it to them.

744
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:37,280
Yes.

745
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:38,320
Your Ladyship.

746
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:40,800
We're looking forward to your work.

747
00:31:41,120 --> 00:31:43,000
We'll go ahead.

748
00:31:43,120 --> 00:31:44,640
Amber, see them off.

749
00:31:44,760 --> 00:31:45,560
Yes.

750
00:31:55,360 --> 00:31:57,120
Your Ladyship, look.

751
00:31:57,280 --> 00:31:58,680
Look at them.

752
00:31:58,960 --> 00:32:00,480
They all have their intentions.

753
00:32:00,560 --> 00:32:02,440
They all have ulterior motives.

754
00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:04,160
Who knows

755
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:05,720
what their intentions are?

756
00:32:05,800 --> 00:32:07,600
You shouldn't have thanked them.

757
00:32:07,680 --> 00:32:09,360
Why did you thank them?

758
00:32:09,360 --> 00:32:10,440
-All right.
-Who knows...

759
00:32:10,520 --> 00:32:11,640
All right.

760
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:12,920
You may go too.

761
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:14,160
His Lordship will be back soon.

762
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:14,880
After he returns,

763
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:16,720
Her Ladyship must still serve him.

764
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:18,000
Go.

765
00:32:18,080 --> 00:32:19,000
Your Ladyship, look at them.

766
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:20,040
Go.

767
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:23,760
All day long,

768
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:25,640
