778
00:32:50,200 --> 00:32:51,480
how can she provide an explanation

779
00:32:51,560 --> 00:32:53,120
to Great Madam and Her Highness?

780
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:03,040
Your Ladyship.

781
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:03,760
Did you see

782
00:33:03,880 --> 00:33:05,000
