They're obviously looking down on us.

784
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:08,800
Peacock among the flowers?

785
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:09,760
It's nice,

786
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:11,320
but it's last year's design.

787
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:12,920
They're not even embarrassed
to show it to us.

788
00:33:14,120 --> 00:33:15,480
It's just Concubine Qiao's plan

789
00:33:15,560 --> 00:33:17,360
