799
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:34,880
an opportunity to pull tricks?

800
00:33:35,040 --> 00:33:36,360
Silly girl.

801
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:37,000
Have you forgotten

802
00:33:37,120 --> 00:33:38,240
