803
00:33:40,480 --> 00:33:42,960
Your Ladyship wants to use this matter

804
00:33:43,040 --> 00:33:44,760
to check their embroidery items?

805
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:48,120
In over a year,

806
00:33:48,120 --> 00:33:48,720
we got

807
00:33:48,760 --> 00:33:50,040
a few clues.

808
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:51,360
It's just that too many people

809
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:52,640
