he didn't defend the coast well?

822
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:28,680
How can I forget?

823
00:34:29,920 --> 00:34:32,560
Official Hu showed me a great favor.

824
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:35,546
Yet I couldn't do anything when he
encountered difficulties.

825
00:34:35,560 --> 00:34:36,620
(Fan Weigang)

826
00:34:36,640 --> 00:34:38,920
Now, his only daughter Liansong

827
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:40,520
